sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(EPP/Gateway)
    participant TLS as TLS Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Validator as AllowlistValidator<br/>(SSRF Protection)
    participant Connector as NIXL v2 Connector
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller vLLM<br/>(remote pod)
    participant Decoder as Local Decoder vLLM<br/>8001/TCP localhost
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2 Protocol)

    Client->>TLS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port=host:port<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    TLS->>Validator: Validate prefiller target
    Validator->>Validator: Check x-prefiller-host-port<br/>against InferencePool pod IPs

    alt Prefiller IP not in allowlist
        Validator-->>Client: 403 Forbidden<br/>"prefiller address not allowed"
    end

    Validator-->>TLS: Validated OK
    TLS->>Connector: Route via P/D connector

    Note over Connector,Prefiller: Phase 1: Prefill (KV-cache population)
    Connector->>Connector: Clone request<br/>Set max_tokens=1<br/>Set stream=false<br/>Add kv_transfer_params<br/>  do_remote_decode=true<br/>Generate x-request-id UUID
    Connector->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP(S) (optional TLS 1.2+)<br/>Modified request with KV params
    Prefiller-->>Connector: 200 OK<br/>Response with kv_transfer_params:<br/>  remote_block_ids<br/>  remote_engine_id<br/>  remote_host, remote_port

    Note over Connector,Decoder: Phase 2: Decode (token generation)
    Connector->>Connector: Build new request<br/>Restore original max_tokens<br/>Attach prefiller KV metadata<br/>Preserve x-request-id
    Connector->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP(S)/8001 (optional TLS 1.2+)<br/>Request with KV transfer metadata
    Decoder-->>Connector: 200 OK<br/>Generated tokens (stream or batch)
    Connector-->>Client: HTTPS Response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No Prefill Header)

    Client->>TLS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>No x-prefiller-host-port header<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    TLS->>Decoder: Passthrough proxy<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
    Decoder-->>TLS: 200 OK Response
    TLS-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Validator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: SSRF Allowlist Update (Background)

    Validator->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Validator: InferencePool spec<br/>(label selectors)
    Validator->>K8sAPI: Watch Pods matching selectors<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Validator: Pod add/update/delete events
    Validator->>Validator: Rebuild allowlist<br/>(host IPs from pod status)
